contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|Indonesian|indonesian}} The word '''Indonesian''' may refer to: * Anything of, from, or related to [[Indonesia]], a country in Southeast Asia, including Indonesian people * [[Culture of Indonesia]], a complex of original indigenous customs and multiple foreign influences * [[Indonesian language]], locally known as ''Bahasa Indonesia'', the official language of Indonesia * [[Indonesian cuisine]], diverse cuisine from Indonesia's approximately 6,000 populated islands ==See also== *[[List of Indonesians]], specific Indonesian persons * [[Demographics of Indonesia]] {{disambiguation}}
